 */
---

<section id="about" class="what-is" aria-labelledby="what-is-heading">
  <div class="what-is__inner">
    <h2 id="what-is-heading" class="what-is__heading">
      <span class="what-is__heading-lead">What is</span>
      <span class="what-is__heading-name">Caracal?</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="what-is__lede">
      Caracal turns ambient credentials into short-lived, signed mandates that
      authorize each agent action before any code runs.
    </p>

    <div class="what-is__grid">
      <a class="what-is__card" href="/concepts/mandate/">
        <span class="what-is__card-glyph" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2 4 6v6c0 4.4 3.4 8.4 8 10 4.6-1.6 8-5.6 8-10V6l-8-4Z" />
            <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="what-is__card-title">Mandates</h3>
        <p class="what-is__card-body">
          Short-lived, signed authority objects scoped to a principal, policy,
          and intent. The replacement for long-lived API keys.
        </p>
        <span class="what-is__card-cta">Read the model →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="what-is__card" href="/concepts/policy/">
        <span class="what-is__card-glyph" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M4 6h16" />
            <path d="M4 12h16" />
            <path d="M4 18h10" />
            <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="2.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="what-is__card-title">Policies</h3>
        <p class="what-is__card-body">
          Declarative rules evaluated at the gate. Every action is permitted,
          denied, or constrained: deterministically and explainably.
        </p>
        <span class="what-is__card-cta">Author a policy →</span>
      </a>

      <a class="what-is__card" href="/concepts/audit-ledger/">
        <span class="what-is__card-glyph" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3.5" y="4" width="17" height="16" rx="2" />
            <path d="M7.5 9h9" />
            <path d="M7.5 13h9" />
            <path d="M7.5 17h6" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="what-is__card-title">Audit</h3>
        <p class="what-is__card-body">
          Every decision recorded in an append-only ledger. Replay any agent
          run, prove compliance, and revoke authority instantly.
        </p>
        <span class="what-is__card-cta">Audit & replay →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
